:"625332575b76538c5623a3eb54c533cd3d1fad87","tid":109261,"uid":47966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T00:39:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>台灣咪又係遲早...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n台灣係你有生之年都唔會俾共產黨搶到，死心啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n緊係喇，國民黨同共產黨本是同根生，從一開始就係偽國民真土共，又點會俾人搶，因為根本冇必要"},{"pid":"f7db7935d2f89c5e490768eda77f6fe45f17d553","tid":109261,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T00:40:09.000Z","msg":"節奏慢咁多 唔易適應"},{"pid":"d49b3b08c956851a97a19adf54f7260201ae4d6b","tid":109261,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T00:51:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>台灣咪又係遲早...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n台灣係你有生之年都唔會俾共產黨搶到，死心啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n緊係喇，國民黨同共產黨本是同根生，從一開始就係偽國民真土共，又點會俾人搶，因為根本冇必要</blockquote><br />\n民進黨唔係台獨黨<br />\n只係資進黨 <br />\n兩岸政策跟國民黨差別唔大"},{"pid":"b0af646c7bd3cd0771e39656f3a56c202c443ef4","tid":109261,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T01:35:58.000Z","msg":"支那廿年<br />\n香港玩完"},{"pid":"98c67bf7ea3d76a69c8ecd193937454abc9581eb","tid":109261,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T01:38:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>台灣咪又係遲早...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n台灣係你有生之年都唔會俾共產黨搶到，死心啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n緊係喇，國民黨同共產黨本是同根生，從一開始就係偽國民真土共，又點會俾人搶，因為根本冇必要</blockquote><br />\n起碼<br />\n台灣仲有得選總統<br />\n有軍隊<br />\n經濟自主<br />\n其實分別好撚大<br />\n話冇必要根本就錯晒<br />\n搶唔到就搶唔到啦"},{"pid":"5f0d01814a32c2db29b4be5ceb72c48afacb8124","tid":109261,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06